# WeatherDemo

WeatherDemo is an Android application that reads and displays sensor data such as temperature, pressure, and light. This project demonstrates the use of Android sensors and Kotlin programming.

## Features

- Display ambient temperature
- Display atmospheric pressure
- Display light levels
- Real-time updates


## Installation

To get a local copy up and running follow these simple steps:

### Prerequisites

- Android Studio
- Git

### Clone the Repository

```sh
git clone https://github.com/hassanshameel/WeatherDemo.git
cd WeatherDemo
